com.w2.api.engine.robots.connection

Class RobotConnectionException

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.w2.api.engine.robots.connection.RobotConnectionException

  • public class RobotConnectionException
extends java.lang.Object
    'RobotConnectionException' indicates exceptions related to Failed connection to a robot. It encapsulates the 'APIException' related to the failure and also the last 'RobotConnectionState' of the 'Robot'
